1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:02,000
Yuki! Why are you running?!

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,170
Are you an idiot?
I'm suspended right now!

3
00:00:04,170 --> 00:00:05,710
If they'd seen me there,
I would've been expelled!

4
00:00:05,710 --> 00:00:08,170
Oh yeah, you're right.

5
00:00:08,170 --> 00:00:09,630
I'm sorry...

6
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:11,470
Yuki, have a seat.

7
00:00:11,470 --> 00:00:12,600
Huh?

8
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,560
This outfit really does
suit you better, Yuki.

9
00:00:26,110 --> 00:00:28,360
I can do it myself.

10
00:00:29,150 --> 00:00:32,910
I'm a prince, after all.
Doesn't this feel a bit like Cinderella?

11
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:35,540
What are you talking about?

12
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:39,290
I'm sorry I forgot about what happened when we were kids.

13
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:43,710
Yuki, when did you realize?

14
00:00:44,090 --> 00:00:46,000
The first time we met.

15
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:51,930
But back then,
I just thought you looked familiar.

16
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,010
The scar you got from saving me...

17
00:00:56,810 --> 00:01:00,060
I can't believe it's still there.

18
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:02,230
It turned into a serious wound, didn't it?

19
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:07,480
I must have looked so lame back then, huh?

20
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:09,240
You were so cool.

21
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:14,240
I only ever tried to act cool
in front of Yu-kun, who I barely got to see.

22
00:01:15,490 --> 00:01:19,700
So even back then,
you were already making me your prince, Yuki.

23
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:25,170
Makoto...

24
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,880
I...

25
00:01:34,090 --> 00:01:36,010
Makoto... my feelings for you...
